<L>__{interior connie's house day}
<A>__{this is the house where mama lives with connie's children, connie so rarely is there. he steps in; his mother is asleep in a chair in the living room. he moves to her, and bends low, whispers.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{mom... mom...}
<A>__{she opens her eyes, which are red and small with age.}
