<D>__{tell me, when pop had troubles... did he ever think, even to himself, that he had gone the wrong way; that maybe by trying to be strong and trying to protect his family, that he could... that he could... lose it instead?}
<C>__{mama}
<P>__{(sicilian)}
<D>__{you talk about the baby. she can have another baby.}
